    <h1 class="display-4 text-center">NSW Servo Moduli</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">NSW Servo Moduli bilan Precise Burchakli Harakatni Nazorat qiling</p>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Umumiy Ma'lumot</h2>
        <p>NSW Servo Moduli servo motorlarini boshqarish uchun mo'ljallangan. Bu modul robototexnika, avtomatlashtirish tizimlari va boshqa turli xil loyihalarda keng qo'llanilishi mumkin. U Arduino va boshqa mikrokontrollerlar bilan mos keladi.</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_servo.jpg" alt="NSW Servo Moduli" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Asosiy Xususiyatlari</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Ishlash kuchlanishi: 4.8V-6V DC</li>
            <li>Burchak nazorati: 0°-180°</li>
            <li>Modul hajmi: 30 x 20 x 10 mm</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Ilovalar</h2>
        <p>NSW Servo Moduli quyidagi turli loyihalarda ishlatilishi mumkin:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Robototexnika</li>
            <li>Avtomatlashtirish Tizimlari</li>
            <li>RC Avtomobillar va Uchuvchilar</li>
            <li>DIY Gadjetlar</li>
            <li>Ta'lim Loyiha</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Pin Tafsilotlari</h2>
        <p>NSW Servo Moduli portida quyidagi pinlar mavjud:</p>
        <table class="table table-bordered">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Pin</th>
                    <th>Vazifasi</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>GND</td>
                    <td>Manfiy to'k</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>VCC</td>
                    <td>Quvvatlantirish manbai</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Signal</td>
                    <td>Servo boshqarish signali</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>NSW Servo Moduli RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_servo_rj25.jpg" alt="NSW Servo RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning Signal pinini PWM pinga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_servo_dupont.jpg" alt="NSW Servo Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, NSW Servo Modulini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
#include &lt;Servo.h>

Servo myservo;
const int servoPin = 9;

void setup() {
    myservo.attach(servoPin);
    Serial.begin(9600);
}

void loop() {
    for (int pos = 0; pos &lt;= 180; pos += 1) {
        myservo.write(pos);
        delay(15);
    }
    for (int pos = 180; pos >= 0; pos -= 1) {
        myservo.write(pos);
        delay(15);
    }
}
        </code></pre>
